{"tid":124032,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（柒到喊）為吸引陌生女子注意 男子高處墮下骨折","createTime":"2017-02-17T09:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T09:27:55.000Z","uid":3514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a666af97ebfbbd4466adbe4aed99f5fc3e7c9ec7","tid":124032,"uid":3514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:25:50.000Z","msg":"為咗溝女，你可以去到幾盡？外國就有位男士為咗吸引女仔注意，搞到跌斷手！<br />\n<br />\n根據英國《每日郵報》早前報道，呢位男士喺室內見到一位女士騎住自動扶手電梯嘅左側扶手上，並且擺弄自己條裙，佢為咗奪得呢位咁奇特嘅女子歡心，竟然有樣學樣，騎上右側扶手上。不過佢千算萬算都估唔到，自己會失去平衡，不慎墜落。成個人跌落一樓地板上，好彩佢只係手臂骨折，冇咩大礙。<br />\n<br />\n屌，條友一開波以為自己好撚型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8084e0b92e6791fbbd78aee3ba5bd6c837aeaa","tid":124032,"uid":3514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"屌，漏撚咗條source，自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://sina.com.hk/news/article/20170217/1/67/20/%E5%9E%8B%E5%88%B0%E7%9B%A1%E9%A0%AD%E4%BE%BF%E6%98%AF-%E7%82%BA%E5%90%B8%E5%BC%95%E9%99%8C%E7%94%9F%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E9%AB%98%E8%99%95%E5%A2%AE%E4%B8%8B%E9%AA%A8%E6%8A%98-6956860.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20170217%2F1%2F67%2F20%2F%25E5%259E%258B%25E5%2588%25B0%25E7%259B%25A1%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E6%2598%25AF-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%25BC%2595%25E9%2599%258C%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2584%258F-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%25A2%25AE%